**Description 75: Nominal and Real Interest Rates (1970-2010)**
- **Left graph** (USA Nominal Interest Rate): blue (10-year bond yield), red (short rate)
- Both peak ~15-20% around 1980, decline to near 0% by 2010
- **Right graph** (USA Real Yield): solid blue (actual), dashed red (estimated)
